---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Authors — LiwoxDotNet"
  description="Meet the author behind LiwoxDotNet"
>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24 max-w-3xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Authors</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg">
        The mind behind LiwoxDotNet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Author Content -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-16">

      <p>
        LiwoxDotNet is built and maintained by 
        <a 
          href="https://armstrong.liwox.net" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block bg-foreground text-background px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition"
        >
          Armstrong Uzoagwa
        </a>, 
        a DevOps engineer focused on building scalable digital systems and real-world platforms.
      </p>

      <p>
        With a strong background in cloud infrastructure, automation, and system design, Armstrong builds solutions that go beyond simple websites — focusing instead on full systems that are reliable, scalable, and production-ready.
      </p>

      <p>
        Through LiwoxDotNet, he helps businesses turn ideas into working platforms using modern tools, clean architecture, and efficient deployment strategies.
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Focus Areas -->
    <div class="border-t pt-16 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Focus Areas</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl mb-3">⚙️</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Designing scalable platforms using modern DevOps and cloud infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl mb-3">☁️</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Cloud</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Building and deploying reliable cloud-native applications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl mb-3">🚀</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Execution</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
            Turning ideas into real systems that are deployed, tested, and scalable.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>
